"title": "5691: friends, good",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5691",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those whose commitment from the heart is shown in practical, often sacrificial, care, love and service. They are a source of encouragement, sympathy, comfort and support in time of need. Such relationships are to be cultivated, especially among believers.</p>\n<h2>Examples of good friends</h2>\n<h3>David and Jonathan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:1-1Sam18:3\">1SA 18:1–18:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:17\">1SA 20:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:42\">1SA 20:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:26\">2SA 1:26</a></p>\n<h3>Job's friends</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11\">JOB 2:11</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Ruth and Naomi</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16-Ruth1:17\">RUT 1:16–1:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Paul's friends in ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:3-Rom16:5\">ROM 16:3–16:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:12-2Cor2:13\">2CO 2:12–2:13</a> <em>Titus</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:25\">PHP 2:25</a> <em>Epaphroditus</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:7\">COL 4:7</a> <em>Tychicus</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:14\">COL 4:14</a> <em>Luke</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:2-2Tim1:4\">2TI 1:2–1:4</a> <em>Timothy</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:1\">PHM 1:1</a> <em>Philemon</em></p>\n<h3>Other examples</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:23\">1SA 22:23</a> <em>David and Abiathar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:2\">2SA 10:2</a> <em>David and Nahash</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:19-2Sam15:21\">2SA 15:19–15:21</a> <em>David and Ittai</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:32-2Sam15:37\">2SA 15:32–15:37</a> <em>David and Hushai</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:1\">1KI 5:1</a> <em>David and Hiram</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:2\">2KI 2:2</a> <em>Elijah and Elisha</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:15\">2KI 10:15</a> <em>Jehonadab and Jehu</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:3-Mark2:4\">MRK 2:3–2:4</a> <em>the friends who brought the paralysed man to Jesus Christ</em></p>\n<h2>The benefits brought by good friends</h2>\n<h3>Comfort and sympathy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11-Job2:13\">JOB 2:11–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:17\">PRO 17:17</a></p>\n<h3>Support and encouragement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:16-1Sam23:17\">1SA 23:16–23:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:24\">PRO 18:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:9-Eccl4:10\">ECC 4:9–4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:10\">PRO 27:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:11-Eccl4:12\">ECC 4:11–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:3\">AMO 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:55-Matt27:56\">MAT 27:55–27:56</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1\">MAT 28:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:11-Rom1:12\">ROM 1:11–1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Sacrificial service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:7\">ROM 5:7</a></p>\n<h3>Shared joy and sorrow</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:5\">LUK 15:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:15\">ROM 12:15</a></p>\n<h3>Loving rebuke</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:6\">PRO 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:9\">PRO 27:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a></p>\n<h3>Encouragement in good works</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:13\">ROM 14:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24\">HEB 10:24</a></p>\n<h3>Challenge</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:17\">PRO 27:17</a></p>\n<h2>Good friendship among believers</h2>\n<h3>Unity in the love and fear of the LORD</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:63\">PSA 119:63</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:16\">MAL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:1\">PHP 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>Worshipping together</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:13-Ps55:14\">PSA 55:13–55:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps133:1\">PSA 133:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42-Acts2:43\">ACT 2:42–2:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:46–2:47</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing possessions</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44-Acts2:45\">ACT 2:44–2:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:35\">ACT 4:32–4:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:29\">ACT 11:29</a></p>\n<h3>Serving together</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:8-Gal2:9\">GAL 2:8–2:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:3-Phil1:5\">PHP 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Praying for one another</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:10\">JOB 42:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11-2Thess1:12\">2TH 1:11–1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>Living peaceably</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:18\">ROM 12:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:2-Phil4:3\">PHP 4:2–4:3</a></p>\n<h3>Covering sins</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:12\">PRO 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:28\">PRO 16:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:9\">PRO 17:9</a> <em>A friend does not stir up trouble by spreading details of wrongs suffered, but rather seeks reconciliation</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:6\">1CO 13:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:8\">1PE 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Restoring from sin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1-Gal6:2\">GAL 6:1–6:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:19-Jas5:20\">JAS 5:19–5:20</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the friend of sinners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:19\">MAT 11:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:34\">LUK 7:34</a></p>",
